{{Top|leg}}
The '''Irden''' tribe was one of three prominent tribes of the [[Ugnaught/Legends|Ugnaught]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Gentes/Legends|Gentes]]. The other two known tribes were the [[Isced]] and the [[Botrut]]. [[Ecclessis Figg/Legends|Ecclessis Figg]] brought many Irden Ugnaughts to his [[Tibanna/Legends|tibanna]]-mining facilities in [[Cloud City/Legends|Cloud City]] on the nearby planet [[Bespin/Legends|Bespin]], where they lived in the southern section of the [[Mining Quarter]].

